DivaDotNet is a simple library to manipulate resouces on "DIVA.NET" with Ruby.
With this library, you'll be able to get your high-scores easily.

A feature of this library is that any other gems are unnecessarry.
You simply have to put a few files into your directory to get resources on "DIVA.NET."
See "sample.rb" to know usage of this library.

DivaDotNet is currently maintained by @tondol (http://twitter.com/tondol/).
DivaDotNet source code is published on GitHub: http://github.com/tondol/divadotnet/
